# Project Overview

This is a Phaser 3 game project built with Remix, React, and TypeScript. The application is a multiplayer game with WebSocket communication for real-time updates.

## Main Entry Points
- [app/root.tsx](mdc:app/root.tsx) - Main entry point for the Remix application
- [app/entry.client.tsx](mdc:app/entry.client.tsx) - Client-side entry point
- [app/entry.server.tsx](mdc:app/entry.server.tsx) - Server-side entry point

## Key Application Files
- [app/app.client.tsx](mdc:app/app.client.tsx) - Main client application component with Phaser game integration

## Project Structure
- `app/routes` - Contains all the application routes using the Remix flat routes convention
- `app/components` - Reusable React components
- `app/game` - Phaser game-related code
- `app/services` - Services for API calls and WebSocket communication
- `app/store` - State management using Zustand
- `app/types` - TypeScript type definitions
- `app/utils` - Utility functions
